duties_responsibilities.duty: Accountable for high performing daily operations in the assigned central fulfilment unit through the external service partner that operates the unit.
Analyzing market trends, identifying growth opportunities, and refining strategies.
Managing the company's online presence through the External Service Partner.
Leading, steering, planning, supporting, and following up the operations and the development of the distribution organization within the unit.

education_certification.credential: University degree (Economics, Logistics, Supply Chain Management) or proven performance in logistics/commercial/supply chain management
